data.description: Welcome. This peaceful single-family home is nestled on an expansive 2.74-acre lot, offering you ample space. Situated near Falcon amenities, it ensures you are not far from convenience.  The property is zoned for horses, making it a haven for equestrian enthusiasts.    Step inside and be greeted by the inviting vaulted ceilings that create an airy and spacious atmosphere. The home has been thoughtfully renovated and meticulously maintained, ensuring a modern and comfortable living experience. Updated bathrooms add a touch of luxury and functionality to this charming abode.    The property features a convenient 2-car garage, providing shelter for your vehicles and additional storage. The flat lot offers ease of movement and showcases breathtaking views of Pikes Peak. Imagine waking up to the sight of this majestic mountain every day.    Beyond the confines of the house, you'll find yourself surrounded by the beauty of Colorado's landscape. The generous acreage gives you endless possibilities—whether you want to create a flourishing garden, set up outdoor recreational activities, or simply bask in the openness and tranquility of the countryside.    This residence offers a perfect blend of modern living and the beauty of nature. It's not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Come and experience the serenity, comfort, and possibilities that this property on Clifford Drive has to offer.
